(1)design the head section
The metadata can be used by browsers (how to display content or reload page), search engines (keywords), or other web services.

charset = "UTF-8" 
specify the character encoding of the html page in this case "UTF-8"

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
we set the width to divice width and the zoom level to 1

HTML5 declaration <!DOCTYPE HTML> 
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meata name="viewport" content=" width=device-width , initial-scale = 1.0"/>

